summary: This is an email from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York regarding the production of an FBI 302 interview report (Fernandez_302.pdf) to the defense in a case, inquiring about the existence of a protective order.

persons.name: Assistant United States Attorney
persons.context: Author of the email, working in the Southern District of New York, discussing the production of an FBI 302 report to the defense.

keyFacts: An FBI 302 interview report regarding an individual named Fernandez (Fernandez_302.pdf) is being discussed for production to the defense.
The prosecutor inquires whether a protective order is in place in the case before producing the document.
The communication indicates coordination between prosecution and defense regarding evidence disclosure in September 2019.
